<item>
            <title>[DATAREST-565] Hal Browser does not seem to work with spring boot with a non-default context-path</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-565</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;if i have server.contextpath=foo in my application.properties &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and i go to localhost:8080/foo/ i am redirected to localhost:8080/browser/index.html which is 404. It if i navigate to: localhost:8080/foo/browser/index.html it also redirects me to that same place. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hal Browser needs to take context path into account.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
